      <t>This document defines a YANG data model and associated mechanism enabling subscriber's adaptive subscriptions to a publisher's event streams with various different period intervals to report updates. Applying these elements allows servers automatically adjust the volume of telemetry traffic sent from publisher to the receivers and keep it within a specified maximum rate of traffic.</t>
